<b><big><u>Property Description</u></big></b><br><br>
Relax, your search is over. Welcome home to The Summit at Chino Hills. Enjoy the comforts of home within this beautiful community in Chino Hills, California. Nestled in the Chino Hills, CA foothills, The Summit offers contemporary one- or two-bedroom apartment homes and a suite of community amenities, such as a clubhouse, fitness center, dog park, pool, spa, package concierge lockers and much more. Our apartment homes feature the highest quality appointments and all the little details that define timeless living.<br><br>We are across the street from the Ridgeview Trailhead, which offers stunning views of the surrounding mountain ranges and valleys. If you prefer mountain biking on weekends or a leisurely stroll, Chino Hills State Park offers over 60 miles of trails and is minutes away from our community.<br><br>Need to upgrade your wardrobe or just a good brunch spot? The Shoppes at Chino Hills is a five-minute drive and offers an array of boutique retailers and upscale eateries.<br><br>Sitting just off Chino Hills Parkway, our community is exceptionally well-located within Chino Hills. We are around the corner from Carbon Canyon, which provides convenient access to North Orange County. We are minutes from the 60 Freeway, which facilitates easy commutes to either Los Angeles or Riverside. You could use the 57 or 91 Freeways to head into either Central or South Orange County.<br><br>We invite you to experience the spectacular lifestyle we have to offer. Discover why our apartment homes embody everything we love about Chino Hills, CA. Call today to schedule a personal tour, and make The Summit your next home!<br><br>
